parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause various electrical accessories to malfunction, including headlights, windshield wipers, turn signals, and air conditioning, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The ignition switch gets stuck in the "on" position
the key does not return to the "run" position
the starter remains engaged when the vehicle is running

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the airbag light illuminating on the dashboard, indicating a potential failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on while driving
no warning or indication of the malfunction before the light comes on
the airbag may be inoperative in the event of a vehicle accident.
